&lt;p&gt;As seen in the other answers:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;pre class=&quot;lang-py s-code-block&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;hljs language-python&quot;&gt;df.groupby([&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-string&quot;&gt;&apos;Fruit&apos;&lt;/span&gt;,&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-string&quot;&gt;&apos;Name&apos;&lt;/span&gt;])[&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-string&quot;&gt;&apos;Number&apos;&lt;/span&gt;].&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-built_in&quot;&gt;sum&lt;/span&gt;()

